title: Freshwater Fishing: Steelhead Seasonal Tactics
description:
Title: Steelhead Seasonal Tactics

1989

By: World Class Sportfishing, and Inter Global Video Promotions Ltd.

Language: English

An instructional video on steelhead fishing, filmed in Canada.

Dubbed from VHS tape to DVD with separate player and recorders, using highest quality setting consistent with DVD disk size, Then converted to .avi using Auto GK, to create a file of about 700MB
